CMS for Scouts ... more infos coming soon


INSTALL:
- Rename db.conf.sample to config/db.conf.php and fill your data
- Edit LINK_MAIN in config/path.conf.php
- Import last file from sqldump/
- Set chmod 0777 for uploads/ (in some cases you must set chmod for subdirectories to!) & tmp/
- Set title and some other in template/layout.php
- Use impeesa! ;) (Defaultadminuser: DasLampe (Password: Test123))

ScoutNet-Calender:
if you like to use the ScoutNet-Calender, you must set our ID in pages/models/calender.php (Line 22)